---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SiteFooter from "../components/SiteFooter.astro";
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from "../data/site";

const CONTACT_PHONE_DISPLAY = "0475 624 247";
const CONTACT_PHONE_TEL = "+61475624247";

const lastUpdated = new Intl.DateTimeFormat("en-AU", {
  day: "numeric",
  month: "long",
  year: "numeric",
}).format(new Date());
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Screwdriver Marketing"
  description="How Screwdriver Marketing collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal information when you use our website, forms, quizzes, or contact us."
>
  <div class="relative min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">
    <header class="relative z-10 border-b border-[var(--border)] bg-bg-deep/80 backdrop-blur-md">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 sm:px-6">
        <a href="/" class="group flex items-center gap-2">
          <span
            class="font-display flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-accent-glow text-lg font-extrabold text-bg-deep shadow-lg shadow-accent/20 transition group-hover:scale-105"
            aria-hidden="true">S</span
          >
          <span class="font-display text-lg font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-xl">
            Screwdriver <span class="text-accent">Marketing</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-muted transition hover:text-cream">← Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="relative z-10 px-5 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20">
      <article class="legal-prose mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="font-display mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <p class="mt-8 leading-relaxed">
          Screwdriver Marketing respects your privacy and is committed to handling your personal information responsibly.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect personal information when you use our website, complete a form, book a call, or contact us.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect personal information you provide to us, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>your name</li>
          <li>business name</li>
          <li>email address</li>
          <li>phone number</li>
          <li>website or Google Business Profile link</li>
          <li>information you submit through forms, quizzes, audits, or enquiries</li>
          <li>details about your business, services, reviews, marketing, or online presence</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We may also collect basic website usage information through tools such as cookies, analytics, advertising pixels, and similar technologies.
        </p>
        <p>This may include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>pages visited</li>
          <li>time on site</li>
          <li>device and browser information</li>
          <li>approximate location</li>
          <li>referral source</li>
          <li>advertising or campaign interactions</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How we use your information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>provide your requested audit, health check, snapshot, or recommendations</li>
          <li>contact you about your enquiry or form submission</li>
          <li>book and manage calls</li>
          <li>provide marketing, website, reputation management, automation, or related services</li>
          <li>improve our website, advertising, and services</li>
          <li>follow up about relevant services that may help your business</li>
          <li>maintain records and manage client relationships</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Marketing and follow-up communication</h2>
        <p>
          If you submit a form or request information from us, we may contact you about your request, your results, recommendations, and related services.
        </p>
        <p>You can opt out of marketing communications at any time.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>For email, use the unsubscribe link if provided or contact us directly.</li>
          <li>For SMS, reply STOP to opt out.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Commercial electronic messages in Australia generally need consent, must identify the sender, and must include a way to unsubscribe.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Cookies, analytics, and advertising tools</h2>
        <p>We may use third-party tools to understand website activity and improve our marketing, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Meta Pixel</li>
          <li>Google Analytics</li>
          <li>Google Tag Manager</li>
          <li>GoHighLevel or similar CRM/marketing tools</li>
          <li>website hosting and analytics providers</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These tools may collect information about how you use our website and may use cookies or similar technologies.
        </p>
        <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

        <h2>5. Disclosure to third parties</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>
        <p>
          We may share information with trusted service providers who help us operate our website, manage enquiries, deliver services, run advertising, host data, or communicate with you.
        </p>
        <p>These may include providers for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>website hosting</li>
          <li>analytics</li>
          <li>CRM and email/SMS systems</li>
          <li>advertising platforms</li>
          <li>payment processing</li>
          <li>calendar booking</li>
          <li>business operations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We may also disclose information if required by law.</p>

        <h2>6. Storage and security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable steps to protect personal information from misuse, loss, unauthorised access, modification, or disclosure.
        </p>
        <p>
          However, no online system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Accessing or correcting your information</h2>
        <p>
          You may request access to the personal information we hold about you or ask us to correct inaccurate information.
        </p>
        <p>To do this, contact us using the details below.</p>

        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy questions, access requests, corrections, or unsubscribe requests, contact:</p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-cream">Screwdriver Marketing</strong><br />
          Email: <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a><br />
          Phone: <a href={CONTACT_PHONE_TEL}>{CONTACT_PHONE_DISPLAY}</a><br />
          Location: Adelaide, South Australia
        </p>

        <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will be published on this website.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </article>
    </main>

    <SiteFooter />
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-syne);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .legal-prose p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .legal-prose ul {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .legal-prose li {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-prose a {
    color: var(--signal);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .legal-prose a:hover {
    color: var(--cream);
  }
</style>
